attributes.title: Podcast But At The Most Pretentious College
attributes.description:
Feeling insecure? You should be, because we’re at Georgetown University! Guests include a well-dressed yet humble young man hoping to make a difference in government, a surgeon grandpa with his future-surgeon granddaughter, and a couple of gals who solely use dating apps to waste people’s time. Recorded on October 8th, 2021 at Georgetown University in Washington, DC.

attributes.title: Podcast But On Venice Beach w/ Trevor Wallace
attributes.description:
Put on your tourist shoes and get ready for some totally random experiences because after 3 years we finally went to the Venice Beach Boardwalk! We teamed up with California hero Trevor Wallace and chatted with a shy kid from Canada, a Native American construction worker who loves life on the Rez, and a guy who's "big in the punk rock scene" going through a big punk rock divorce that's tearing the punk rock community apart. Filmed on 1/25/22 on the Venice Beach Boardwalk in Venice, CA.

attributes.description:

attributes.title: Podcast But OUTSIDE The Apple Store (While INSIDE The Big Apple!) w/ Cole Escola
attributes.description:
Start spreadin’ the newwwwsss, we set up in front of your iPhone’s mommy: The Apple Store! Actor and comedian Cole Escola joins us as we talk to strangers. Guests include a New York architect who brags about what he’s built, a young Lithuanian actress dying to play a psychopath, and a Lorde-obsessed gay man who’s going to be the next greatest dancer. Also featuring the insane story of how Cole (the host) got his cat. Recorded on 10/10/21 in Brooklyn, NY.

attributes.title: Podcast But On Wall Street! (the money place)
attributes.description:

attributes.title: Podcast But In Times Square!
attributes.description:
Nietzsche theorized that “Time is a flat circle,” but we proved that dork wrong as hell— cause guess what! Time’s Square! Guests include an artist excited about having her first public art sculpture debut right in Times Square, a handwriting-obsessed couple on their way to the Opera, and Crazy Boi C-Reezy, a bike-loving guy who’s just trying to influence the youth to join the two-wheeler movement. Recorded 10/11/21 in New York City.
